  "texts": [
    "The scope of this paper is parameter estimation in snow hydrology, with a focus on snow coverage mapping and snow depth, indicated with an A(left) and I (right) in Figure 2.",
    "The figure showcases a combination of different elements in order to achieve a comprehensive solution.",
    "A involves the combination of image sensors, 165 hydrology parameter, and machine learning/deep learning.",
    "B, on the other hand, merges image sensors with snow cover mapping.",
    "C unites snow cover mapping and snow depth estimation, while D links snow depth estimation and ML/deep learning."
  ]
}